area_name: Jon Guinther's GoogleEarth Maps of Sundown
pathTokens: Jon Guinther's GoogleEarth Maps of Sundown

content.description: Re-Organization Note 7/20/20 - All of the routes originally in this sub-area have been moved to the newly created sub-areas.Â I have renamed this page to preserve the GoogleEarth Maps that Jon created, as they may help in some regard, although sketch maps have been placed in each sub-area. Many thanks to Jon Guinter who submitted these routes with photographs, and who gave permission for the routes to be re-organized.Original write-up by Jon:There are many boulders surrounding the main Sundown Ledge area. I spent a few days finding and cleaning some awesome problems, but there's a lot more potential! I gave everything my own names, but I'm sure some of these have been climbed before. Please comment and criticize my names/grades if you've climbed these before!
